{"tid":1501371,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黃秋生寸警：有乜後顧之憂","createTime":"2019-08-24T10:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T11:18:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ea6d4d1ff2caaccf754b332863414575e57e7638","tid":1501371,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:44:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190824/20754844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190824%2F20754844&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=6b3a943c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190824%2F20754844&h=a0bbe2eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190824/20754844</a><br />\n<br />\n黃秋生寸警：有乜後顧之憂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190824/large/1566570251_a62b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190824%2Flarge%2F1566570251_a62b.jpg&h=cb3b8e12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n秋生在fb反問警員：「做警察好醜咩？」資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警員及速龍小隊在執勤時，疑多次濫用武力卻未有展示警員編號，市民投訴無門。監警會副主席張華峰昨日在訪問時，竟聲稱：「執法時無後顧之憂。」黃秋生昨日在fb發文，他反問：「若警員可以唔展示警員編號，咁市民點解要出示身份證？唔出示編號係因為可以無後顧之憂，請問若警員依法辦事，有乜後顧之憂？」<br />\n<br />\n秋生不明白警方為甚麼會突然擔憂起來：「如果唔出示編號唔出示委任證，個個指吓個鼻話我係差人都得啦。做乜咁驚畀人知你真係警察呢？做警察好醜咩？證明身份係保障警員，亦保障冇人可以冒警。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：霍琪 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n田蕊妮被無綫踢出宣傳<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n梁競徽遊故宮表忠"},{"pid":"3ab02b4e74e7f22ca621a9ce2aa603f95491bff7","tid":1501371,"uid":136334,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:48:57.000Z","msg":"撚狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17fd556f496ccf9201a0674a04d90de076ea9a0c","tid":1501371,"uid":137588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:49:22.000Z","msg":"返送中白色恐怖大事記<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1500277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1500277</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6fa426dae7a41978b4f5bf267c05e39a7b45e157","tid":1501371,"uid":157535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"全民冒警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8389be59c11996464bab10c3680feb96c3ab78","tid":1501371,"uid":114891,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:12:55.000Z","msg":"黃秋生做警司果陣已經好有風骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d080115a9207fc79972e76580b7eef08fd202d90","tid":1501371,"uid":222262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:15:23.000Z","msg":"火麒麟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bcb94988cd09bbcd673b8b61a886e683ed969a6","tid":1501371,"uid":249480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:18:42.000Z","msg":"生秋黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}